================================================================================
MODIFICATIONS
================================================================================

The following substantial modifications have been made to create Urasi:

1. Complete technology stack migration:
   - Backend: Laravel → Supabase (PostgreSQL + Edge Functions)
   - Frontend: Vue.js → React 18 + TypeScript
   - Styling: Legacy CSS → TailwindCSS 4
   - Build: Webpack → Vite 7

2. Architecture changes:
   - Monolithic → Client/Server separation
   - MySQL → PostgreSQL with real-time capabilities
   - Server-side rendering → Single Page Application

3. Feature additions and customizations:
   - Modern UI components (Radix UI)
   - Enhanced real-time updates
   - Custom business logic modifications

